  • Method Details

    • onPrePersist

      public void onPrePersist()
      Method that gets invoked before insertion. Sets the operation type to save, marks as active, and fills in the create and update date values.

    • onPreUpdate

      public void onPreUpdate()
      Method that gets invoked on update. Sets the operation type to update, and updates the update date value.

    • onPreRemove

      public void onPreRemove()
      Method that gets invoked before deletion. Sets the operation type to delete, marks as inactive, and updates the update date value.
